{
  "text": "(See, e.g., [CITATION_1] .) Thus, the quadratic action (10) with (11) and (12) offers us a unifying framework to study the propagation of GWs in parity violating theories of gravity described above. The concrete forms of α(t) and β(t) depend on the background cosmological evolution of a(t) and φ(t) as well as the theory under consideration.",
